c: 10
v: 89
t: "qal allah taealaa lhma: qad 'ujibat daewatukuma fi fireawn wamalayih wa'amwalihim -wkan musaa ydew, waharun ywmmin ealaa deayh, famin huna nusibat aldaewat 'iilaa alathnyn- fastaqima ealaa dynkma, wastmrra ealaa daewatukuma fireawn waqawmuh 'iilaa tawhid allah wtaeth, wala tslka tariq man la yaelam hqyqt wedy wweydy"